Excuse me.

207
00:15:08,541 --> 00:15:10,583
Could we have a word with you?

208
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:11,416
[NATSUKI]
Who're you?

209
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:12,375
A friend.

210
00:15:12,458 --> 00:15:14,083
My name's Haruto Tsukishiro.

211
00:15:14,166 --> 00:15:16,750
And I'm Katsumi Kanzaki.

212
00:15:16,833 --> 00:15:18,416
[NATSUKI]
You won't trick me.

213
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:20,125
You're really ghosts!

214
00:15:20,208 --> 00:15:21,541
We are not ghosts!

215
